<!DOCTYPE section SYSTEM "mingle_help.dtd">
<section title="Create cards with the blue plus icon" id="create_cards_using_quick_add_card">
	<p>
		Very similar to the <cref topic="creating_cards_with_quick_add_card">quick add card</cref>, the blue "+" icon at the top of all columns on any <cref topic="grid_view">grid view</cref> allows you to quickly create a new card that will appear within the column you're adding it to.</p> 
  <p>To create a new card using the feature, simply click on the blue "+" icon and enter the card title in the pop-up that appears.</p>
	<p><screenshot src="resources/images/new_add_card.gif"/></p>	
</section>